27:52.171 --> 27:53.737
and I'll get your
schedule all worked out?

27:53.739 --> 27:56.241
Tomorrow it is, Professor X.

28:03.514 --> 28:06.048
Oh hey, Lisa, you
work here, too?

28:06.050 --> 28:08.886
No, I just hang
out here, a lot.

28:10.021 --> 28:12.923
So what's up with
Todd and Clark?

28:12.925 --> 28:14.624
I don't think
that's gonna work out.

28:14.626 --> 28:18.461
I mean, Clark is,
uh, into DC Comics.

28:18.463 --> 28:19.528
What's wrong with DC?

28:19.530 --> 28:21.431
Superman, Batman.

28:21.433 --> 28:25.167
- Todd is a Marvel man.
- How much so?

28:25.169 --> 28:27.170
Well, you could ask his dogs,

28:27.172 --> 28:28.805
Stan and Lee.

28:28.807 --> 28:31.441
Ouch.

28:31.443 --> 28:32.942
Well, speaking of going out,

28:32.944 --> 28:34.644
are you seeing anyone?

28:34.646 --> 28:35.481
Me, no.

28:37.383 --> 28:38.749
Why is that so absurd,

28:38.751 --> 28:40.549
