28:40.551 --> 28:43.519
It's just, people
don't ask me out.

28:43.521 --> 28:44.453
How long has it been

28:44.455 --> 28:46.789
since someone asked you out?

28:46.791 --> 28:48.557
Two years.

28:48.559 --> 28:50.093
Two years?

28:50.095 --> 28:53.262
You're a human female who
hangs out in a comic shop,

28:53.264 --> 28:54.530
and you're single?

28:54.532 --> 28:55.865
There's no way.

28:55.867 --> 28:57.933
It's just I'm
not very interested

28:57.935 --> 28:59.568
in the guys who hang out here,

28:59.570 --> 29:01.637
and it probably shows.

29:01.639 --> 29:03.272
I'm sure it does.

29:03.274 --> 29:06.143
So would you like to go
out with me sometime?

29:06.145 --> 29:08.178
What, you mean like get
a group of gals together

29:08.180 --> 29:11.314
and have like a
girls' night out?

29:11.316 --> 29:13.749
