more like dinner.

29:13.751 --> 29:15.551
I know this really cool bistro

29:15.553 --> 29:16.920
down in the Flats.

29:16.922 --> 29:19.189
This bitchin' lesbian
couple owns it.

29:19.191 --> 29:20.891
That way, you can hold
a pretty girl's hand

29:20.893 --> 29:24.094
over dinner and nobody
looks at you weird.

29:24.096 --> 29:25.329
Oh, that, um.

29:26.665 --> 29:28.164
I, uh.

29:28.166 --> 29:29.399
Look, if I'm not your
type, you can let me know.

29:29.401 --> 29:30.636
I'm a big girl.

29:31.837 --> 29:33.838
- I'm not gay.
- Oh shit.

29:36.474 --> 29:39.310
- I am so sorry.
- It's okay, really.

29:40.511 --> 29:42.445
I tried feelin'
you out verbally,

29:42.447 --> 29:43.646
and then when you
said you weren't

29:43.648 --> 29:45.115
into the guys at the shop...

29:45.117 --> 29:46.549
It's really okay.

29:46.551 --> 29:49.986
I'm actually really
flattered that you'd ask.

29:49.988 --> 29:52.955
Why not, you're
super funny, smart,

29:52.957 --> 29:54.459
- and cute.
- Thanks.

29:55.993 --> 29:57.661
Well, look, if I haven't
already made you feel

29:57.663 --> 29:59.061
massively uncomfortable,

29:59.063 --> 30:00.529
how 'bout I make it up to you?

30:00.531 --> 30:01.998
Dinner.

30:02.000 --> 30:05.367
Maybe not the bistro, but
Denny's, Taco Bell, whatever.

30:05.369 --> 30:08.305
Even though we can't be
more than just friends?

30:08.307 --> 30:10.406
Well there's no just about it.

30:10.408 --> 30:12.108
I'd be happy to be your friend.

30:12.110 --> 30:13.477
You're fascinating.

30:13.479 --> 30:15.211
And I'd like to get
to know you better.

30:15.213 --> 30:16.214
As a friend.

30:17.415 --> 30:19.281
I'd like that, too.

30:19.283 --> 30:20.650
Well, look, I gotta boogie.

30:20.652 --> 30:23.452
Let Kevin know I'll be
here in the morning.

30:23.454 --> 30:24.622
Sure.

30:31.363 --> 30:32.929
Where's Carley?

30:32.931 --> 30:34.163
She had to go.

30:34.165 --> 30:36.499
She said she'd be
in tomorrow morning.

30:36.501 --> 30:39.269
- She's incredible.
- Yeah, she's really cool.

30:39.271 --> 30:40.503
Yeah.

30:40.505 --> 30:42.571
She's like an expert
in every comic.

30:42.573 --> 30:45.942
