too soon after Ashley.

31:07.098 --> 31:08.698
I get it.

31:08.700 --> 31:11.902
But, Lisa, I'm a man
of the 21st century,

31:11.904 --> 31:16.573
and information nowadays
moves at the speed of light.

31:16.575 --> 31:20.009
Wait to long and an
opportunity can pass you by.

31:20.011 --> 31:22.278
Think she has a guy?

31:22.280 --> 31:25.981
Oh, I don't think any
guy could interest her.

31:25.983 --> 31:29.486
Right, she does have that
unattainable vibe about her.

31:29.488 --> 31:33.056
But, hey, odds weren't in my
favor for dating my cousin.

31:33.058 --> 31:36.593
So, odds must not
apply in my life.

31:36.595 --> 31:39.628
- Odds are that...
- Hey, I gotta go call Mark,

31:39.630 --> 31:41.830
and let him know
what's goin' on.

31:41.832 --> 31:43.066
It's a good thing I told him

31:43.068 --> 31:45.234
