portion of Star Fleet.

32:46.697 --> 32:48.367
That's a good one.

32:49.867 --> 32:51.134
All right, everybody start out

32:51.136 --> 32:53.502
with your early
sci-fi writer sets.

32:53.504 --> 32:55.438
And set out any Isaac
Asimovs, Heinleins,

32:55.440 --> 32:57.943
or Arthur C. Clarkes you have.

33:00.111 --> 33:01.443
