41:31.189 --> 41:32.988
Who was
your date anyways?

41:32.990 --> 41:35.091
This chick Stephanie.

41:35.093 --> 41:39.263
That wouldn't happen to
be Stephanie Lane, would it?

41:40.131 --> 41:40.962
Wait a minute, am I,

41:40.964 --> 41:42.901
am I in a reality show?

41:43.834 --> 41:45.700
How do you know that?

41:45.702 --> 41:47.569
Oh my God, don't you know?

41:47.571 --> 41:49.305
She's a famous blogger.

41:49.307 --> 41:50.406
Stephanie Lane?

41:50.408 --> 41:52.073
- So?
- So, do you know

41:52.075 --> 41:53.642
what her blog is called?

41:53.644 --> 41:54.843
Enlighten me.

41:54.845 --> 41:56.745
It's called Parade of Losers.

41:56.747 --> 41:58.046
It's about her love life,

41:58.048 --> 42:00.816
