54:31.535 --> 54:32.968
AK?

54:32.970 --> 54:34.336
Yeah, AK.

54:34.338 --> 54:35.339
After Kirby.

54:37.575 --> 54:39.408
Well, we do try to
keep the store going,

54:39.410 --> 54:40.978
even in the AK era.

54:42.111 --> 54:44.011
Attention,
attention, everyone.

54:44.013 --> 54:46.682
As you may know, my
name's Kevin Murphy.

54:46.684 --> 54:49.517
And tonight we have a very
special lady in the house.

54:49.519 --> 54:52.787
She has came to mean
a lot to the store.

54:52.789 --> 54:54.455
